{
    "chapterId": "Act01_Chapter04_Trial",
    "lines": [
        {
            "id": "line_2",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "很可疑啊，看不懂的档案加上没有一点蛛丝马迹的房间",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "唯一的线索还是与C息息相关宗教项链，我只能认为房间是你精心布置后的样子",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_4",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "说起来之前都是你在指认啊。不知不觉陷入你的话术里去了",
            "portrait": "A/老囚2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_5",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "的确，太多疑点集合在你身上了，后续言语如有冒犯，还请海涵",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_6",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "（啧，这下麻烦了）",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_7",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "首先请回答，为什么会有十字架项链出现在你的房间里",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_8",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "RequireEvidence",
            "parameters": [
                "十字架",
                "line_9",
                "line_13"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_9",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "还解释什么？这根本就不是我的东西",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_10",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "那你们能解释出你们牢房里的十字架物品吗？\n只能说是C给我们每人都交换了宗教内物件，身为传教士来说很合理把，况且我也是基督教信徒",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_11",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "哈？你什么时候又成基督信徒了？",
            "portrait": "A/老囚2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_12",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "我一直都是啊？不然你以为我怎么进来的？",
            "portrait": "Player/主角2",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_12_jump",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": ["line_15"]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_13",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "这个理由能说服你们吗",
            "portrait": "Player/主角2",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_14",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "你觉得呢？",
            "portrait": "A/老囚2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_14_sus",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": ["D", "25"]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_15",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "那..那档案怎么解释，为什么就你一个人的档案是乱码",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_16",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "（看来只有我才能看见，该怎么才能蒙混过关？）",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_17",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "这你不该问我，典狱长不是在旁边吗？",
            "portrait": "Player/主角2",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_18",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "这点我也无法解释，档案不是我写的",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_19",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "伪人拥有改变其他人认知的能力，如果你是伪人的话就都说得通了",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_20",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "（不好，这样下去对我很不利！）",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_21",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "果然就是你把，赶紧投票了！",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_22",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "RequireEvidence",
            "parameters": [
                "A",
                "line_23",
                "line_26"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_23",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "诸位，我们还记得伪人的特性吗？伪人无法抑制杀人的冲动，假如我真是伪人，某人现在恐怕不会站在这里吧",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_24",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "......呜",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_25",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": ["line_28"]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_26",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "等等，这些足够证明我的清白",
            "portrait": "Player/主角2",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_27",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "不，反而成了你在胡编乱造的依据",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_27_sus",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": ["D", "25"]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_28",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "的确如果你真的是伪人，A是不可能打得过你的",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_29",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "刚刚的对话，反而在我的脑海中拼凑出了整个案发过程，让我们继续讨论吧！在到达真理前无法回头",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_30",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "我先来还原一下案发过程把\nC离开B房后，像往常一样回房间注射药物，在这期间被伪人杀害",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_31",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "我与他无冤无仇，不可能冒险去做这种事",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_32",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "的确，除非有死亡笔记，不然很难做到在没有外伤的情况下杀了C",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_33",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "我看未必",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_34",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "ShowChoice",
            "parameters": [
                "A|branch_a_start",
                "B|branch_b_start"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_a_start",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "你真的干不出来吗？",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_35",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "不可能，绝对不可能！我没有杀他的动机",
            "portrait": "A/老囚2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_36",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "RequireEvidence",
            "parameters": [
                "酒瓶",
                "branch_a_success",
                "branch_a_fail"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_a_success",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "不，你的动机很纯粹，而且证物就放在你的房间里不是吗\nC先在B房传教，回房间时被喝醉了的你遇到，并与你约定——用卷轴换酒。可C食言了，这就是你的动机",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_37",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "什么！！？",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_38",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": ["A", "25"]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_39_jump",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": ["trial_end"]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_a_fail",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "这就是你去C房间的动机",
            "portrait": "Player/主角2",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_40",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "没看出来那处是动机",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_41",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "耍我呢！",
            "portrait": "A/老囚2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_42",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": ["D", "25"]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_43",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": ["trial_end"]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_b_start",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "的确，人类确实没有这种能力，但是“伪人”可以\nC是在看见了某种东西后导致的心脏麻痹",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_44",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "RequireEvidence",
            "parameters": [
                "黑皮书",
                "branch_b_success",
                "branch_b_fail"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_b_success",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "狂热的教徒终于见到了真主，但是虚伪的假象摧毁了神父的信仰",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_45",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "你是说C是因为过于激动导致病发",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_46",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "正是，但我们之中见过真主画像的，只有你B\n只有你昨天可能看来黑皮书！",
            "portrait": "Player/主角2",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_47",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": ["B", "25"]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_48",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": ["trial_end"]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_b_fail",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "没错就是看见了这些",
            "portrait": "Player/主角2",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_49",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "哼哼哼...哈哈哈哈哈哈\n抱歉失态了，我真是高估你了，没想到为了洗脱嫌疑什么都能编得出来",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_50",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "够了，不要再胡搅蛮缠",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_51",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": ["D", "25"]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_52",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": ["trial_end"]
        },
        {
            "id": "trial_end",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "审判的时钟已经敲响\n刽子手已就绪，该送行了。",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_54_load",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "LoadScene"
        }
    ]
}